main event: A Project Blue Book report from October 1965 discusses unidentified aerial objects.
interesting points: The report indicates no unidentified aerial objects have threatened national security., The Air Force finds no evidence of technological advances beyond current scientific knowledge., There is no indication that UFOs are extraterrestrial vehicles., Unidentified aerial objects are categorized into known and unknown., The Air Force will continue to investigate UFO sightings for national security implications.
